sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant X as Client
  participant I as InsForge Auth
  participant C as Control Service
  participant P as Policy Layer
  participant E as Execution Service

  U->>X: Sign in
  X->>I: Authenticate
  I-->>X: Access token / session
  X->>C: API request with bearer token
  C->>I: Verify token / claims
  I-->>C: Valid identity
  C->>P: Resolve permissions
  P-->>C: Authorization decision
  C-->>X: Run accepted / gate result
  C->>E: Issue scoped execution token
  E-->>C: Execution outcome
